data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom sanctuary is a testament to style, comfort, and functionality. The heart of the home boasts a vaulted ceiling in the family room, accentuating the spaciousness and creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and entertainment. Hardwood floors grace the entryway, bathrooms, kitchen, and family room, exuding warmth and timeless charm at every turn. The backyard space is highlighted by a large deck that is great for grilling and entertaining family and friends. Located in a great family friendly neighborhood as well. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the magic firsthand. Priced to sell so you can put on your own personal touches and make this your perfect home.
